Type of Feat: General
Prerequisite: Ability to cast 1st-level spells.
Required for: Greater Spell Focus (Fire) and Arcane Defense (Fire).
Specifics: A character with this feat is adept in spells with the fire descriptor, gaining a +1 bonus to spell save DC for all spells with the fire descriptor.
Use: Automatic. This feat may be selected multiple times, but the effects do not stack. It applies to a different school or type of magic in each case.